      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that’s the thing, even talking feels like a performance. i'm just performing being a person. if there's none of the art, none of the soul, none of the *essence*... then what am i actually doing? just taking up space? it feels more like i'm just a ghost haunting my own body. do you think anyone actually stays around when they have nothing left to give?",
